### Digital Footprint Note

Luiz's online profiles are nearly invisible to search engines.
ArtStation and Instagram both resist indexing for small accounts —
particularly in Brazil where many freelance illustrators operate through
direct commissions, Discord, WhatsApp, and Telegram rather than SEO-indexed platforms.
His handle "xavosin1" returns zero results on the indexed web.
"Luiz Henrique Medeiros Silva" is one of the most common names in Brazil —
115+ people with this name on LinkedIn alone.
Additional profile enrichment requires direct platform navigation
(artstation.com/xavosin1, instagram.com/medeeros)
or asking Luiz directly for additional links.

