## The Luiz × Marwan Pixel Art Experiment

Evan asked Marwan to convert Luiz's illustration into pixel art.
It didn't translate — the styles were fundamentally incompatible.
Neither artist created friction about it.
No tension documented on Luiz's side.

**The lesson:**
Luiz's painterly illustration style is its own thing.
Don't try to make it into something else.
The EIW line and the Outside Inn line are distinct by design —
Luiz serves one, Marwan serves the other,
and the brand is stronger for keeping them separate.

