## Araguari, MG — Geographic Context

Araguari is a mid-size city in the Triângulo Mineiro region of Minas Gerais, Brazil.
Population approximately 120,000.
Regional university center is Universidade Federal de Uberlândia (UFU),
located ~30km away in Uberlândia — the most likely institution
for someone in Araguari pursuing visual arts or design.
IFTM (Instituto Federal do Triângulo Mineiro) has a distance-learning presence
in Araguari but no confirmed on-site campus.
No academic records for Luiz were found in any Brazilian database.
Education background remains unconfirmed — add directly from Luiz.

